        <abstract>
            <p>Agrees that in a deaf person the jaw may fall because of concentrated attention.</p>
            <p>In surprise, mouth is opened suddenly and chest filled with air. This expression occurs in all parts of the world. Odd that so simple a movement is so perplexing to understand.</p>
        </abstract>
